<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <ety>[from <ets>M</ets>icrowave
<ets>A</ets>mplification by <ets>S</ets>timulated <ets>E</ets>mission of
<ets>R</ets>adiation.]</ety> <def>An electronic device producing
